# Vehicle Specs — on-demand only (cost)

Metered APIs (EPA/catalog, Gemini/LLM, NHTSA recalls for this panel, Auto.dev enrich) must **not** run on estimate page load or idle rail render.

- **UI:** Compact **Specs** CTA (`EstimateLabVehicleSpecsLazy`). Full Fluids/identity dialog loads data **on open**.
- **SSR:** Do not call `getVehicleSpecsBundle` or catalog enrich in estimate panel load paths.
- **Enrichment:** Wire catalog/AI only inside the Specs open/fetch path — never auto-enrich every RO.
- **VIN:** Still not required to show Specs UI; optional for accuracy.

See `agents/ShopRallyCRM/VEHICLE-SPEC-AI-MEMORY.md` § Cost rule.
